 (three-phase orchestration)\n\n#### 5. **docs/USAGE.md** (`/workspace/docs/USAGE.md`)\nComplete CLI usage guide with:\n- **Core concepts** (workflow, step, result, wiring, terminals)\n- **Workflow DSL detailed reference** (step configuration, container blocks, host blocks, wiring syntax)\n- **Step configuration keys:**\n  - `prompt`, `run`, `workflow_name`\n  - `results`, `max_attempts`, `timeout`\n  - `agent_command`, `agent_args`, `feedback`, `prompt_step`\n- **Result protocol** (`CLOCHE_RESULT:<name>` marker format)\n- **Prompt assembly** (step template, user request, validation output, result selection)\n- **Agent command resolution** (priority order, fallback chains)\n- **Workflow locations** (container vs host)\n- **Host step environment variables:**\n  - `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR`, `CLOCHE_STEP_OUTPUT`, `CLOCHE_PREV_OUTPUT`, `CLOCHE_RUN_ID`\n  - `CLOCHE_TASK_ID`, `CLOCHE_MAIN_OUTCOME`, `CLOCHE_MAIN_RUN_ID`\n- **Container environment variables:**\n  - `CLOCHE_RUN_ID`, `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR`, `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `CLOCHE_AGENT_COMMAND`\n- **Complete CLI commands reference:**\n  - `cloche init` — scaffold new project\n  - `cloche run` — launch workflow run\n  - `cloche status` — check run status\n  - `cloche list` — list runs\n  - `cloche logs` — stream logs\n  - `cloche poll` — block until completion\n  - `cloche stop` — cancel run\n  - `cloche delete` — delete container\n  - `cloche health` — per-project summary\n  - `cloche workflow` — list/render workflows\n  - `cloche project` — project info\n  - `cloche get/set` — run context store\n  - `cloche tasks` — task pipeline\n  - `cloche loop` — orchestration loop\n  - `cloche shutdown` — shutdown daemon\n- **Project layout** (`.cloche/` directory structure)\n- **Daemon configuration:**\n  - `CLOCHE_LISTEN` (default: `unix:///tmp/cloche.sock`)\n  - `CLOCHE_DB` (default: `cloche.db`)\n  - `CLOCHE_RUNTIME` (default: `docker`)\n  - `CLOCHE_IMAGE` (default: `cloche-agent:latest`)\n  - `CLOCHE_HTTP` (web dashboard address)\n  - `CLOCHE_AGENT_PATH`, `CLOCHE_LLM_COMMAND`\n  - `CLOCHE_EXTRA_MOUNTS`, `CLOCHE_EXTRA_ENV`\n- **Client configuration:**\n  - `CLOCHE_ADDR`, `CLOCHE_HTTP`\n- **Dockerfile requirements** (cloche-agent, git, agent user, /workspace directory)\n- **Build commands** (make build, test, lint, proto, docker-build, install)\n\n#### 6. **docs/INSTALL.md** (`/workspace/docs/INSTALL.md`)\nInstallation guide with:\n- Prerequisites (Docker, Git, Go 1.25+)\n- Build from source (`make install`)\n- `go install` method\n- Pre-built release binaries (planned)\n- Homebrew installation (planned)\n- Verification steps\n- Upgrade instructions\n\n#### 7. **docs/SAFETY.md** (`/workspace/docs/SAFETY.md`)\nSecurity and safety practices with:\n- **The Lethal Trifecta** (private data + untrusted content + external communication = risk)\n- **Host vs Container workflows** (minimize host-side agent usage)\n- **Network allowlisting** (declare `network_allow` in container block)\n- **Filesystem isolation** (copy-based, no bind mounts, audit overrides)\n- **Credential handling** (pass via env vars, not in images)\n- **Prompt hygiene** (sanitize untrusted inputs, limit feedback)\n- **Review before merge** (check branches before merging results)\n\n#### 8. **docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-versioning-design.md** (`/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-versioning-design.md`)\nProject versioning implementation design with:\n- **Version file:** `.cloche/version` (single decimal integer)\n- **Increment rule:** After evolution Stage 5 (Audit), increment if `len(result.Changes) > 0`\n- **Read path:** `config.LoadVersion(projectDir string) (int, error)`\n- **Surface:** Displayed as `v3` on project detail page\n- **.gitignore:** `.cloche/version` is **not** gitignored (committed with changes)\n- **Changes required:** Evolution orchestrator, config loading, init command, web handler\n\n#### 9. **PROJECT.md** (`/workspace/PROJECT.md`)\nNext features document with:\n- **Orchestration** — auto-picker for \"ready\" tasks, integration with beads, general task tracking adapters\n- **Indicator lights** — status dashboard\n- **Web Dashboard** — project status with indicator lights\n- **Log contents** — capture all output (prompts, scripts)\n- **Container deletion** — keep failed containers, add delete command\n\n#### 10. **AGENTS.md** (`/workspace/AGENTS.md`)\nAgent instructions for developers with:\n- Beads issue tracking (`bd ready`, `bd show`, `bd update`, `bd close`)\n- **Landing the Plane workflow** (session completion requirements):\n  - File issues for remaining work\n  - Run quality gates\n  - Update issue status\n  - **PUSH TO REMOTE** (MANDATORY)\n  - Clean up\n  - Verify all changes pushed\n  - Hand off context\n\n### **Key Documentation Sections Found**\n\n**Versioning:**\n- Version format: `major.minor.build` (semver)\n- CLI flags: `-v`, `--version`\n- gRPC endpoint: `GetVersion`\n- Version bumping policy and project version tracking (`.cloche/version`)\n\n**CLI Flags and Commands:**\n- `cloche -v`, `cloche --version`\n- `cloche init [--workflow <name>] [--base-image <base>]`\n- `cloche run --workflow <name> [--prompt \"...\"] [--title \"...\"] [--keep-container]`\n- `cloche status <run-id>`\n- `cloche list [--all] [--project] [--state] [--limit] [--issue]`\n- `cloche logs <run-id> [--step] [--type] [-f]`\n- `cloche poll <run-id>`\n- `cloche stop <run-id>`\n- `cloche delete <container-or-run-id>`\n- `cloche health`\n- `cloche workflow [--project]`\n- `cloche project [--name]`\n- `cloche get <key>`\n- `cloche set <key> <value|->`\n- `cloche tasks [--project]`\n- `cloche loop [--max] / cloche loop stop`\n- `cloche shutdown`\n\n**gRPC Endpoints:**\n- `GetVersion` (daemon)\n- Bidirectional streaming for `logs` command\n- CLI ↔ Daemon communication via gRPC\n\n**Environment Variables:**\n- Host side: `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR`, `CLOCHE_STEP_OUTPUT`, `CLOCHE_PREV_OUTPUT`, `CLOCHE_RUN_ID`, `CLOCHE_TASK_ID`, `CLOCHE_MAIN_OUTCOME`, `CLOCHE_MAIN_RUN_ID`\n- Container side: `CLOCHE_RUN_ID`, `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR`, `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `CLOCHE_AGENT_COMMAND`\n- Daemon: `CLOCHE_LISTEN`, `CLOCHE_DB`, `CLOCHE_RUNTIME`, `CLOCHE_IMAGE`, `CLOCHE_HTTP`, `CLOCHE_AGENT_PATH`, `CLOCHE_LLM_COMMAND`, `CLOCHE_EXTRA_MOUNTS`, `CLOCHE_EXTRA_ENV`\n- Client: `CLOCHE_ADDR`, `CLOCHE_HTTP`"}],"totalDurationMs":35386,"totalTokens":50693,"totalToolUseCount":13,"usage":{"input_tokens":3122,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14478,"cache_read_input_tokens":30152,"output_tokens":2941,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":14478},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
